{"tid":316973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想講，DSE衰左，真係玩撚完","createTime":"2017-07-11T06:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T10:18:36.000Z","uid":82940,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff61878ddeba3f31ee86fb19f3c519de1000ff1e","tid":316973,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"咁多人講經話衰左唔緊要，讀書唔代表咩<br />\n但我地都知，假設你係窮撚 你就玩撚完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到大學已經要乞食 入唔到大學真係玩撚完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話乜鳩識大把人搵到錢 乜乜乜 咪玩啦 唔否認係有 但一定係少數 如果係咁多 你仲洗讀十幾年書去考個公開試? <br />\n<br />\n如果聽日個分衰撚左 你就玩撚完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過 其實你入唔到神科專科都乞食，香港大撚把文學院撚 bba撚陪你一齊仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結:係香港出世 冇父幹又唔夠聰明 都係一齊玩撚完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffb714884a763709a175a487a5931adb5fcba4e","tid":316973,"uid":59100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689f6fdd0cadd04cff2cc91fd8f9921e7f2046c2","tid":316973,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"你講錯咗 dse衰左唔會玩完 無父幹才是致命"},{"pid":"972f27ae984f44a5609fddabae4009a4af5d60bc","tid":316973,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"3223e3f4f32cdcd16c35fb15fce13378e37f5eaa","tid":316973,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日衰左玩撚完啦成世"},{"pid":"0480cb47eac25138e4923d168e0b2720dfbf3251","tid":316973,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"上年已經衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.